## Limitations

The analysis is based on available data up to early 2025 and may not account for subsequent developments in the natural gas market. Additionally, the geopolitical landscape and weather patterns are inherently unpredictable, which could further influence natural gas prices beyond the scope of this report. The reliance on secondary sources also means that the findings are contingent on the accuracy and timeliness of the reported information.

